- **CPU**: Intel Core i9-9900K (8 cores, 16 threads) - High performance cho parallel processing
- **RAM**: 32GB DDR4 (2x16GB) - Sufficient cho large datasets và multiple applications
- **Storage**:
  - SSD NVMe 1TB (E:) - Primary storage cho n8n data
  - SSD 240GB (F:) - Secondary storage cho temporary files
  - HDD 2TB (D:), HDD 1TB (I:) - Backup storage
- **Network**: Wi-Fi 6, IP: 192.168.1.20 - Stable connection cho API calls
- **Runtime**: Node.js v22.14.0, Docker v27.5.1 - Latest stable versions

## Resource Allocation Guidelines - Practical Balance
- **CPU Usage**: Max 6 cores cho n8n workflows (2 cores reserved cho OS và other applications)
- **RAM Allocation**: 4-8GB cho n8n workflows (24GB+ available cho multitasking)
- **Primary Storage**: E:/n8n-data/ cho all n8n data (SSD NVMe performance)
- **Network Bandwidth**: Wi-Fi 6 bandwidth sufficient cho multiple concurrent API calls

## Performance Capacities - Realistic Expectations
- **Simple workflows**: 50-100 concurrent executions (basic data processing)
- **Medium complexity**: 20-50 concurrent (API integrations, data transformation)
- **Complex workflows**: 10-20 concurrent (AI/ML processing, heavy computations)
- **Resource-intensive tasks**: 5-10 concurrent (large file processing, complex algorithms)

## Storage Strategy - Optimized cho Performance và Organization
- **Primary Data**: E: drive (SSD NVMe) cho database, active workflows, và cache
- **Temporary Files**: F: drive (SSD) cho temporary processing files
- **Backups**: D: hoặc I: drive (HDD) cho regular backups và archives
- **System Files**: C: drive cho OS, applications, và development tools

## Network Configuration - Production Ready
- **Primary Webhook URL**: http://192.168.1.20:5678
